bout one and a half millimeters. This creates enough clearance to eliminate all contact with the platform during rotation. Once this is done, I manually check again that the friction is gone. Only at this point, as a good practice, do I perform a tare recalibration from Iuppiter, to ensure the system starts from an absolute, clean zero. Final tests confirm that the alarms have disappeared." } }" },
